No one can afford that!

137
00:12:12,540 --> 00:12:14,170
Well...

138
00:12:14,170 --> 00:12:16,590
--Then, 100 berries!
--Huh?!

139
00:12:16,590 --> 00:12:18,380
What a deal!

140
00:12:20,880 --> 00:12:23,960
You came down too much! You
have no sense for business!

141
